WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.300 --> 00:00:01.875
At the facility level,

2
00:00:01.875 --> 00:00:04.192
decisions are often made by committees.

3
00:00:04.192 --> 00:00:06.150
The purpose of the facility committee

4
00:00:06.150 --> 00:00:08.142
is to provide the facility's perspective

5
00:00:08.142 --> 00:00:11.898
in determining the best options for managing finances,

6
00:00:11.898 --> 00:00:15.174
and sharing insight regarding those options.

7
00:00:15.174 --> 00:00:17.404
These committees help shape the characteristic

8
00:00:17.404 --> 00:00:20.037
of the institution, provide opportunity

9
00:00:20.037 --> 00:00:23.754
for stakeholder groups to be represented on the committee,

10
00:00:23.754 --> 00:00:25.977
and provide the opportunity for the committees

11
00:00:25.977 --> 00:00:29.928
to oversee all activities associated with the operations

12
00:00:29.928 --> 00:00:31.765
and maintenance of the facility,

13
00:00:31.765 --> 00:00:34.232
including supply chain management.

14
00:00:34.232 --> 00:00:36.908
Facility committees can also provide oversight

15
00:00:36.908 --> 00:00:40.474
on annual budget processes and forecasting.

16
00:00:40.474 --> 00:00:42.215
Select each tab to learn more

17
00:00:42.215 --> 00:00:44.696
about some of these committees.

